---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import AnnouncementBar from '../components/AnnouncementBar.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Opt Out | Hamilton Exteriors"
  description="Opt out of communications from Hamilton Exteriors. Manage your preferences for marketing emails, texts, and other communications."
  noindex
>
  <AnnouncementBar slot="header" />
  <Navbar slot="header" />

  <section class="w-full bg-cream py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-5">
      <h1 class="font-hamilton-display text-[clamp(2.25rem,6vw,3rem)] leading-tight font-normal uppercase text-heading">
        Opt Out
      </h1>

      <div class="mt-12 space-y-8 font-dm-sans text-base/relaxed text-gray-700">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Last updated: March 2026</p>

        <p>We respect your communication preferences. This page explains how to opt out of marketing communications from Hamilton Exteriors and how to request deletion of your personal data.</p>

        <h2 class="font-hamilton-display text-[1.5rem] font-normal uppercase text-heading">Opt Out of Marketing Emails</h2>
        <p>To stop receiving marketing emails from Hamilton Exteriors, you can:</p>
        <ul class="ml-6 list-disc space-y-2">
          <li>Click the "Unsubscribe" link at the bottom of any marketing email you receive from us</li>
          <li>Email us at <a href="mailto:support@hamilton-exteriors.com" class="text-primary underline">support@hamilton-exteriors.com</a> with "Unsubscribe" in the subject line</li>
          <li>Call us at <a href="tel:+16509773351" class="text-primary underline">(650) 977-3351</a> and ask to be removed from our email list</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We will process your email opt-out request within 10 business days. Please note that even after opting out, you may still receive transactional emails related to an active project or service contract (such as appointment confirmations, project updates, or warranty information).</p>

        <h2 class="font-hamilton-display text-[1.5rem] font-normal uppercase text-heading">Opt Out of Phone Calls and Text Messages</h2>
        <p>To stop receiving marketing phone calls or text messages:</p>
        <ul class="ml-6 list-disc space-y-2">
          <li>Reply STOP to any text message you receive from us</li>
          <li>Call us at <a href="tel:+16509773351" class="text-primary underline">(650) 977-3351</a> and ask to be removed from our call and text lists</li>
          <li>Email us at <a href="mailto:support@hamilton-exteriors.com" class="text-primary underline">support@hamilton-exteriors.com</a> with "Opt Out of Calls/Texts" in the subject line, including the phone number(s) you want removed</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We will process your phone and text opt-out request within 10 business days. This will not affect communications related to an active project or scheduled appointment.</p>

        <h2 class="font-hamilton-display text-[1.5rem] font-normal uppercase text-heading">Request Deletion of Your Personal Data</h2>
        <p>As a California resident, you have the right to request that we delete the personal information we have collected about you. To submit a deletion request:</p>
        <ul class="ml-6 list-disc space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Email:</strong> Send a request to <a href="mailto:support@hamilton-exteriors.com" class="text-primary underline">support@hamilton-exteriors.com</a> with "Data Deletion Request" in the subject line</li>
          <li><strong>Phone:</strong> Call <a href="tel:+16509773351" class="text-primary underline">(650) 977-3351</a></li>
          <li><strong>Mail:</strong> Write to Hamilton Exteriors, Inc., 21634 Redwood Rd Unit F, Castro Valley, CA 94546</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Please include your full name and the email address or phone number associated with your account so we can locate your records. We will verify your identity before processing the request.</p>
        <p>Per the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA), we will respond to data deletion requests within 45 days of receipt. If we need additional time, we will notify you and may take up to an additional 45 days. Certain information may be retained as required by law, such as records related to active warranties, completed contracts, or legal obligations.</p>

        <h2 class="font-hamilton-display text-[1.5rem] font-normal uppercase text-heading">Response Timeframes</h2>
        <ul class="ml-6 list-disc space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Marketing opt-out requests</strong> (email, phone, text): Within 10 business days</li>
          <li><strong>Data deletion requests:</strong> Within 45 days per CCPA (with a possible 45-day extension if needed)</li>
          <li><strong>Data access or correction requests:</strong> Within 45 days per CCPA</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-hamilton-display text-[1.5rem] font-normal uppercase text-heading">Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about opting out or managing your communication preferences, please reach out:</p>
        <ul class="ml-6 list-disc space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:+16509773351" class="text-primary underline">(650) 977-3351</a></li>
          <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@hamilton-exteriors.com" class="text-primary underline">support@hamilton-exteriors.com</a></li>
          <li><strong>Mail:</strong> Hamilton Exteriors, Inc., 21634 Redwood Rd Unit F, Castro Valley, CA 94546</li>
        </ul>
        <p>For more information about how we handle your personal data, please see our <a href="/privacy-notice-ca" class="text-primary underline">California Privacy Notice</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="w-full bg-white py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[600px] px-5 text-center">
      <p class="font-dm-sans text-base text-gray-600">
        Have questions about our services?
      </p>
      <a
        href="/"
        class="mt-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-primary px-8 py-3 font-dm-sans text-sm font-semibold text-white transition-colors hover:bg-primary/90"
      >
        Back to Home
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</Layout>
